No Nakadiman Ni Juan A Mamonyag<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.6.14-29">Mk. 6:14-29</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.9.7-9">Lk. 9:7-9</a>)Ki do dawri a chimpo, nadamag ni Āri Herodes<RF q=+>Iyaw nya a Āri Herodes, ki si Āri Herodes Antipas a iyaw anakaw ni Āri Herodes do chimpon nakayanak ni Jesos. No āwag na, ki “tetrako,” as kan no toray na, ki akmay gobirnador. no torayen do Galilya iyaw maynamot di Jesos.
