No Kayam Ni Jesos Do Hapotaw No Ranom<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.6.45-52">Mk. 6:45-52</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?43.6.15-21">Jn. 6:15-21</a>)Do dawri, pinayabang ni Jesos nanawhen na saw a nanma sa a mamtang do dawri a minanga, as iya, ki nabidin pa. Sinpangan na, pinaybidi na saw tawotawowaw do bahabahay da.
