Pyahen San Jesos Maganyit Saw Do Genesaret<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.6.53-56">Mk. 6:53-56</a>)Do nakapakabtang daranaw, nakadok sa Jesos do tana a Genesaret.
