No Makamwamomo A Mangrarayaw<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.24.15-28">Mt. 24:15-28</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.21.20-24">Lk. 21:20-24</a>)Tinongtong ni Jesos naychirin. Binata na a kāna, “Anchan maboya nyonchiw ‘Makamwamomwaw a Mangrarayaw’<RF q=+><a href="tw://bible.*?27.9.27">Dan. 9:27</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?27.11.31">11:31</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?27.12.11">12:11</a> a maytēnek do dyaw a rombeng a paytēnekan na — Inyo a makabāsa so nyaya, awāten nyo a maganay iyaw chakey na batahen! — do dawrinchi, siraw myan do Jodya, machita mayyayo sanchi a somonget do katokotokonan a tomayo.
Iyanchiw myan do papagaw no bahay na, ki dyi dana pakono maybabalay a somdep a mangay a manghap so warawara na a iyonot na.
