Ki an dya inaksayan no Dyos bidang no araw saya a kalidyatan, abanchiw aran sino a mabidin a sibibyay do lobongaya. Ki maynamot dyirad pinidi saw no Dyos, chinsayan naw araw saya a kayan kalidyatanaya.
“Do dawri, an myan makabata sya dyinyo a kāna, ‘Chiban nyo, ari dana dyas Kristo!’ mana ‘Chiban nyo, tori aba dwadaw?’ ki manganohed kamwaba,
