No Mabakes A Napado So Bangbanglo<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.26.6-13">Mt. 26:6-13</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?43.12.1-8">Jn. 12:1-8</a>)Do dawri, myan sa Jesos do Betanya do bahayaw ni Simon a nagliproso do nakarahan. Ki do kadama daw a koman, myan asa mabakes a somindep do bahayaw a nakaigpet so oltimo so kangina a bangbanglo a mayngaran so nardo a nakapno do praskita a alabastro.<RF q=+>Iyaw alabastro, ki kitan bato kan akmay dyidyaw. Tiktikan kan osaren da pangidyidyawan so bangbanglo. Sinpangan na, pinotohan naw alabastrowaw, as nakapado nas bangbanglwaw do ohwaw ni Jesos.
