No Kapachitolag Ni Jodas A Lipotan Na Si Jesos<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.26.14-16">Mt. 26:14-16</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.22.3-6">Lk. 22:3-6</a>)Sinpangan na, si Jodas Iskariote a asa dyirad asaw a poho kan dadwa nanawhen ni Jesos, ki nangay dyirad matotohos saw a papadi tan lipotan nas Jesos.
Do nakadngey daw so rantaw ni Jodas, nasoyot saw papadyaw, kan inkari da dya a torohan das kwarta. Do dawri, insiknan ni Jodas maychichwas so gondaway na a manglipot di Jesos.
No Kaisagāna No Kapanawdyan A Pangmalem<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.26.17-25">Mt. 26:17-25</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.22.7-14">Lk. 22:7-14</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?42.22.21-23">21-23</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?43.13.21-30">Jn. 13:21-30</a>)Do manōmaw a araw no Pista no Tinapay a Abos Libadora<RF q=+>No dāmwaw a pangmalem do dyaya a pista, ki pinangaranan da so Pistan Passover a pakanaknakman da so nakahabasaw no anghil do Egipto.Eks. 12:1-27; Leb. 23:5-8; Deot. 16:5-8 a iyaw no arawaw a kapangdiman dan Jodyo saw so orbon saw a karniro a idāton da, ki inyahes dan nanawhen na saw ni Jesos a kon da, “Dino chakey mo a pagsagānaan namen so pangmalem ta do Pistaya no Nakahabasaw no Anghil?”
Do dawri, tinoboy san Jesos dadwaw a nanawhen na, as kan binata na dyira a kāna, “Somdep kamo do syodadaya, as kan myan anchiw ombayat dyinyo a asa mahakay a mayrara so asa kamalabi a ranom, ki monot kamonchi dya.
Onotan nyonchi do asdepan naw a bahay, as kabata nyonchi syad akin bahayaw a, ‘Ipayahesaw ni Maistro an dino kono kwarto a kanan danchi kan siraw nanawhen naw do kapistaya?’
Ipaboya nanchi dyinyo mamanyitwaw a kwarto a rakoh a nakasagāna dana kontodo lamisaan. Dawrinchiw pagsagānaan nyos kanen ta.”
