No Manawdyi A Kapachipangmalem Ni Jesos Dyirad Nanawhen Naw<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.26.26-30">Mt. 26:26-30</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.22.15-20">Lk. 22:15-20</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?46.11.23-25">1 Kor. 11:23-25</a>)Ki do kayan daw a koman, nanghap si Jesos so tinapay, as nakapaydasal na nagyaman di Āpo Dyos. Sinpangan na, inakchikchid na a intoroh dyirad nanawhen naw, as nakabata na sya dyira a kāna, “Hapen nyo nyaya, ta nyaw inawan ko.”
