Komwan pa dyinyo sichangori. An maboya nyonchiw katongpal no nya saya kalidyatan, chapatak nyo na a masngen danaw kapagtoray no Dyos.
“No ibahey kwaya dyinyo, ki oyod. Myan panchi dyinyo do dyaya kapotōtan sibibyay pa do katongpal no tabon bata ko saya.<RF q=+>Mana “mabo kamo aba a Jodyo sakbay no katongpal a tabo no nya saya a batahen ko dyinyo sichangori.”
Iyanchiw hanyit kan tanaya, ki mabo sanchi a tabo, ki mabo abanchi a polos chirin ko.”<RF q=+><a href="tw://bible.*?19.102.25-27">Sal. 102:25-27</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?23.40.6-8">Isa. 40:6-8</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?40.5.18">Mt. 5:18</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?60.1.24-25">1 Ped. 1:24-25</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?61.3.10-14">2 Ped. 3:10-14</a>
