Ayya! Kabo pan arang nyo. An myan imoha mo a botoh, maypāngo paro katobo na, an dyi pa mahtaw kodit naw.<RF q=+>Myan saw tod a tomobo a botoh a aran dyi pa maimoha. Ki aran komwan, malidyat kapayparakoh na, malaksid an maimoha.
