An mailabeng, ki akmas gagāngayaw a inawan a nainlobongan. Ki an mapagongar dana, asa dana naispiritwan. No chakey na batahen, ki an myan inawan ta a mahta do lobongaya, masigorādo a myan inawan ta a naispiritwan a maitotop do byay tad hanyit.
